$interpreted: Fredrica: Now we're absolutely prepared.
Fredrica: Whatta you think, handsome?
Jerome: With limited supplies and time, to be able to set-up such a multi-faceted event with all this...
Jerome: ...Such a serious general demands one's respect.
Jerome: But, I wanted to ask you...
Fredrica: Yes?
Jerome: I get why you brought so many outfits for the women, but why did you also prepare some for the men...?
Fredrica: Aigh-ya, I don't know~
Fredrica: ...Whatta you say, handsome?
Nigel: Didn't think you'd make it so extravagant...
Nigel: Plus, how'd you convince the demihumans to help you?
Fredrica: Hehe, don't underestimate the allure of a woman.
Fredrica: Okay, the main show is about to begin. I can't wait~
Jerome: Mr. Nigel, perhaps you should say some words...
Nigel: Oh, yes, I...
Nigel: Today, everyone, forget your worries and enjoy this...fair.
Male Demihuman: Can we really...trust the humans?
Female Demihuman: Who knows when the bandits will...
Demihuman Child: Our roof is still leaking...
Jerome: It's not that easy to make everyone relax, is it?
Nigel: ...Oh...
Nigel: An earthquake? What's happening?
Nigel: Perhaps the Dragoneye Gem is...
Male Demihuman: Wah! Look over there!
Nigel: ...The enemy!?
Female Demihuman: Hey, is that Leah and Yamitsuki? How'd they come out of the water?
Leah: Hey hey! Check out these skills!
Leah: Bullseye!
Fredrica: Nice work~handsome!
Fredrica: I hereby announce that the fair has offically begun!
Male Demihuman: Hahaha! What's going on? This is crazy!
Female Demihuman: Looks pretty interesting. Let's take a look, shall we?
Male Demihuman: Okay! Let's have some fun!
Male Demihuman: Wah! Looks delicious!
Izumi: Heehee, you look delicious~Come here~
Jerome: The mushrooms and wild meat are almost gone. The barbecue stand is selling quite well.
Jerome: ...Hey, is that demihuman with the umbrella a guy or a girl...
Jerome: Young Lio, what are you doing over there? Why aren't you playing with everyone?
Lio: I...I'm hiding from my sister.
Jerome: Miss Leah? Why?
Lio: Sis said that since we're twins, if we wear the same outfit, everyone will be happy...
Jerome: ...So you're hiding...
Jerome: Must be tough...
Lio: ...*sob*...
Jerome: Don't worry, we're allies. I won't tell anyone.
Lio: R-Really?
Jerome: Of course. I'm going to bring the rest of the food over. Do you want to come?
Lio: ...Yeah!
Lio: Ah, it's Eve's finale!
Leah: For the finale, let me introduce the two performers~
Leah: In the black corner! She's been protecting everyone from the shadows all along...
Leah: ...the soaring surfer, Ev...YAMITSUKI!!
Leah: And, in the gold corner! Possessing power that lurks beneath the surface...
Leah: ...and butchering skills beyond belief, IZUMI!!!
Fredrica: Let me fill everybody in~All the weapons and outfits everyone is using today were brought to you by the Carterwell family.
Fredrica: Thanks to them, we were able to hold this magnificent fair today. Please, everyone, keep that in mind~
Izumi: Ha, just throwing in the marketing all non-chalant, huh? Flawless strategy~
Izumi: Yamitsuki, let's not be too hard on each other, what do you say?
Yamitsuki: ...To please the crowd, I won't hold back.
Izumi: Wah, what a response~
Izumi: Yamitsuki is really easy to read, just like Nigel!
Yamitsuki: ......
Izumi: Heehee, looks like the fun's over~
Izumi: Then I'll just have to...get more serious.
Izumi: Very impressive, Yamitsuki~
Izumi: Though I'd like to continue, let's stop here.
Yamitsuki: You aren't flustered in the least.
Izumi: Correct~However, everyone is already delighted!
Male Demihuman: Wow, both of them are amazing!
Female Demihuman: Yeah, didn't know Izumi was so powerful~
Male Demihuman: With them and Nigel here, we'll definitely be safe!
Izumi: Boosted everyone's morale without even knowing it~Though it wasn't my original intention...still, not bad.
Izumi: Am I right, Yamitsuki?
Yamitsuki: .........
Yamitsuki: ......Yeah.
Leah: Today's fight...a draw!
Leah: Please, everyone give the two fighters an enthusiastic round of applause!!
Nigel: ......Hmph.
Vicious Bandit: Boss!
Bandit Leader: I've been waiting forever. You weren't discovered?
Vicious Bandit: Nope! Those lowly demihumans are still enjoying their fair. No time to discover us!
Bandit Leader: And as for the horned male?
Scheming Bandit: He's there too. But all his comrades are spread out in the crowd. If it's just up to him, he can't stop us.
Bandit Leader: ...We wanted to lure him out and deal with him alone.
Bandit Leader: Who would have thought that these rats from the kingdom would come out and give us the perfect stage?
Scheming Bandit: A true leader, changing the plan right on the spot.
Scheming Bandit: Not only did you get a good understanding of the enemy's capabilities, but even thought of the genius idea to sneak into the fair!
Bandit Leader: Quit brown-nosing. You're all useless, getting beat down by them. Embarrassing, isn't it?
Vicious Bandit: S-Sorry! They were too powerful...
Bandit Leader: Hmph, forget it. This time, I'll do it myself. Remember, watch for my signal!
Vicious Bandit: Got it!
Bandit Leader: Soon, leader of the demihumans...your treasure, will be mine.
Bandit Leader: Hehehe...MUAHAHAHA!!!
